<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV75">
<l>ulākiṉṟa keṇṭai yoḷiyampe māviyai yūṭuruvak</l>
<l>kulākiṉṟa veñcilai vāṇmukat tīrkuṉi caṅkiṭaṟip</l>
<l>pulākiṉṟa vēlaip puṇariyam paḷḷiyam māṉaṭiyār</l>
<l>nilākiṉṟa vaikunta mōvaiya mōnu nilaiyiṭamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>So that our soul is penetrated by bright arrows, stirring Keṇṭai fish,</l>
<l>you with a bright face with [two] cruel bows that bend, is it Vaikuntam</l>
<l>where stay the servants of the father on the ocean bed with fish-reeking waves</l>
<l>that strike against bent conches, or is the earth the place you reside?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
